1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,399
[SPEAKER_01] Kipa, dobro dan i dobro došli u Novi Čušpać.

2
00:00:02,399 --> 00:00:05,459
[SPEAKER_01] Današnja govša je gospođa Vlatka Vukelić,

3
00:00:05,459 --> 00:00:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] doktornica znanosti, povjesničarka,

4
00:00:08,039 --> 00:00:11,259
[SPEAKER_01] sveučilišna, profesorica i zamalodekanica.

5
00:00:11,259 --> 00:00:12,580
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se moram nasmijet.

6
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] Vlatka, poštovanje, hvala što ste došli.

7
00:00:15,619 --> 00:00:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala na pozivu i pozdrav svim vašim gledateljima i slušateljima.

8
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Svako dobro vama i vašoj obitelji u nove godini.

9
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala također.

10
00:00:24,460 --> 00:00:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] E sad ono, zamalodekanica.

11
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

12
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:28,379
[SPEAKER_01] Sete sami ili?

13
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

14
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:33,759
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi ili vas to ni vaši kontroverzni stavovi za neke koštali tog mjesta?

15
00:00:33,759 --> 00:00:40,600
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, da, to je bio naravno ključ razdora, da tako kažem, s jedne strane.

16
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sa druge strane, ne bih samo rekla kontroverzni stavovi,

17
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] kako se imputiraju, mada ja ne vidim kontroverzu,

18
00:00:50,219 --> 00:00:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo nije u čemu, je li to jedan također specifičan pojam

19
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] o kojem bi se dalo razglabati.

20
00:00:56,799 --> 00:01:02,939
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je ključni problem bila činjenica da ja ne pripadam zapravo nikakvim strukturama

21
00:01:02,939 --> 00:01:07,379
[SPEAKER_00] i da me jako teško u tom smislu kontrolirati.

22
00:01:08,099 --> 00:01:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] A ono što je bio moj imperativ u svemu bila je nekakva modernizacija poslovanja.

23
00:01:13,359 --> 00:01:20,780
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, moja ideja, odnosno ono što sam ja smatrala da smo dosegnuli određeni stupanj zrelosti,

24
00:01:20,780 --> 00:01:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] bila je da se jednostavno mlađoj generaciji, ajmo reći u biti generaciji srednjih godina,

25
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] prepusti upravo taj menadžment kako bi fakultet zapravo postao jedna samoodrživa jedinica.

26
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:41,120
[SPEAKER_00] S obzirom na novi zakon o znanosti, s obzirom na tendencije, da tako kažemo,

27
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:47,040
[SPEAKER_00] u razvoju znanosti, ali određenog koncepta inovacija u visokoškolskom obrazovanju,

28
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] moja ideja je bila promijeniti pristup. Upravo kako bi, kao što sam rekla,

29
00:01:53,819 --> 00:01:59,780
[SPEAKER_00] fakultet postao samoodrživa jedinica bez tolikog oslanjanja financijskog na, ne znam,

30
00:01:59,780 --> 00:02:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ministarstva znanosti i obrazovanja. Da sam bila u pravu, zapravo podatak je i o sve većem broju

31
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] privatnih sveučilišta u Republici Hrvatskoj, koja postaju značajan takmac u biti javnim sveučilištima

32
00:02:16,099 --> 00:02:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] i oduzimaju nam dio studenta, a samim time zapravo i dio radnih mjesta.

33
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] Uz radna mjesta idu i projekti, dakle, govorimo o jednom zatvorenome krugu.

34
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:33,240
[SPEAKER_00] U tom smislu, ja sam smatrala da društveno-humanistički koncept

35
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:41,379
[SPEAKER_00] Fakulteta Hrvatskog studija, na kojem mi i počivamo, da on može biti i tekako produktivan

36
00:02:41,379 --> 00:02:47,379
[SPEAKER_00] društveni segment. A ne da se zadrži, kako ja to volim reći, na onom konceptu

37
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:54,180
[SPEAKER_00] znanstvenog larpulartizma, gdje mi kao znanstveno osoblje sami jednim drugima nešto pričamo,

38
00:02:54,180 --> 00:03:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nema onaj rič, nema onaj doseg u javnosti i nema društvenu korisnost.

39
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] E to je bila tendencija koju sam ja htjela promijeniti pod broj jedan i pod broj dva.

40
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:13,879
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo, mišljenjem je bilo da trebamo vratiti fokus na studenta kao ključnog aktera u tom procesu.

41
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne u smislu da bi student donosio neke važne odluke za instituciju, ali da prilagodimo svoje programe,

42
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] da ih osuvremenimo, da vidimo što su nove generacije, dakle da se napravi temeljita analiza

43
00:03:31,139 --> 00:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] i da im se prema tome u biti ponude i ono što mi zovemo izlazne kompetencije, jel?

44
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:45,419
[SPEAKER_00] Da postanemo atraktivni, da vidimo je li njima bolji pristup ako rade više u praksi

45
00:03:45,419 --> 00:03:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] ili je bolji pristup teorijske naravi, jel?

46
00:03:48,819 --> 00:03:52,879
[SPEAKER_00] Ili nešto što se uklapa u njihov mindset.

47
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:57,620
[SPEAKER_00] Nedavno sam bila na roditeljskom sastavanku Najmlađeg Čeri

48
00:03:57,620 --> 00:04:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo je pedagoginja na predavanju rekla da više zapravo ne mjerimo

49
00:04:02,539 --> 00:04:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] generaciju unutar kronološkog razdoblja od desetak godina,

50
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] kako smo nekada gledali, jel, generacijski ciklus,

51
00:04:11,819 --> 00:04:16,120
[SPEAKER_00] već da se taj ciklus kojim označavamo određenu generaciju,

52
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, skratio na tri godine.

53
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] De facto to znači da vi morate prilagođavati svoje programe,

54
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] pristupe, jel, pedagoški standard, u puno kraćem razdoblju.

55
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,060
[SPEAKER_00] Tri puta manje.

56
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako je, tako je.

57
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:36,399
[SPEAKER_00] I zapravo oni usvajaju gradiva na nekim drugačijim principima.

58
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] Meni su, ne znam, ova generacija ove godine

59
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:42,540
[SPEAKER_00] je bez ikakve nelagode postavila pitanje

60
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:45,600
[SPEAKER_00] mogu li oni pisati svoje seminarske radove

61
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,319
[SPEAKER_00] uz pomoć umjetne inteligencije.

62
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,360
[SPEAKER_01] To sam ti joj pital, da.

63
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:51,879
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali, pazite, oni uopće, oni nemaju srama od toga.

64
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:55,899
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nemaju nelagode u smislu da je to nekako plagijatstvo,

65
00:04:55,899 --> 00:04:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] lažno autorstvo ili bilo što drugo.

66
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,759
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Njima to nitko nije objasnio.

67
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:03,860
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, tu konkretno, mi kao znanstvena nastavna zajednica

68
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:06,620
[SPEAKER_00] možemo se postaviti na način da kažemo

69
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] ok, treba uvesti dio predmeta, bilo obaveznih, bilo izbornih,

70
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] različiti su pristupi, koji će se baviti tipa medijskom

71
00:05:17,019 --> 00:05:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] i informacijskom pismenošću.

72
00:05:19,779 --> 00:05:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da se njih nauči da svaka informacija koju daje AI,

73
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] na primjer, nije pouzdana ili točna.

74
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sad prije, prije neki dan sam tražila nešto.

75
00:05:32,699 --> 00:05:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zanimala me literatura o jednom specifičnom fenomenu

76
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] i provela sam, to je umobolnost s moje strane,

77
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:44,819
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono, tri sata u svađi sa umjetnom inteligencijom.

78
00:05:44,819 --> 00:05:48,920
[SPEAKER_01] Moj kamerman diže dva prsta jer je on meni jučer lekciju

79
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,439
[SPEAKER_01] održao nešto ovaj. Ja sam nešto pitao isto

80
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,759
[SPEAKER_01] i dobio sam takvu citabu ovaj, da.

81
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako. Upravo to.

82
00:05:55,600 --> 00:06:00,680
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ono, tri sata protratiš jer ti on upravo ne daje

83
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,120
[SPEAKER_00] konkretan odgovor koji ti tražiš.

84
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ga ja pitam o jednom fenomenu

85
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] i on meni odgovara, veli, ali to je korpus općeg znanja.

86
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:14,160
[SPEAKER_00] Pa rekao, dobro, ali odkuci ga ti izvukao.

87
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:16,399
[SPEAKER_00] I sad on meni počne davati članke,

88
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:18,399
[SPEAKER_00] kao znanstvene članke,

89
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:21,040
[SPEAKER_00] koje ja kad sam ih počela otvarati,

90
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,399
[SPEAKER_00] vidim da opće ne odgovaraju naslovu i autoru

91
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi on predložio i onda shvatim da opće ne postoje

92
00:06:27,259 --> 00:06:29,540
[SPEAKER_00] ni ti autori, ni ti članci.

93
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:32,839
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, okej, ja uvjetno rečeno znam problematiku,

94
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] pa znam da je AI ušao u fazu takozvanih halucinacija,

95
00:06:37,259 --> 00:06:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] da je počeo izmišljati.

96
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:39,800
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, to je legtivo.

97
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ali Rino ima odgovor, bude ga on ovaj.

98
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] Šta si mi napisao, bude mi ovaj.

99
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:47,600
[SPEAKER_00] E, ali recimo djete od 18 godina

100
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,399
[SPEAKER_00] koje možda nije toga svjesno

101
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] i kojemu je kroz medije

102
00:06:51,019 --> 00:06:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] stalno nameta na nekakva teza

103
00:06:54,139 --> 00:06:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] da je AI super,

104
00:06:55,519 --> 00:06:58,060
[SPEAKER_00] da to pojednostavljuje procese učenja,

105
00:06:58,060 --> 00:06:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] da mu to pomaže, ne znam,

106
00:06:59,779 --> 00:07:01,620
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo na razini mentalnih mapa.

107
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:03,639
[SPEAKER_00] On neće biti toliko kritičan

108
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] prema tome sadržaju i apriorno će ga

109
00:07:05,819 --> 00:07:07,240
[SPEAKER_00] akceptirati, jel?

110
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] E, u tom smislu,

111
00:07:09,379 --> 00:07:10,860
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sad da se vratim na početak

112
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:12,060
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo vašeg pitanja, jel?

113
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam htjela u tom smislu

114
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] dakle ponuditi nešto novo

115
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:20,560
[SPEAKER_00] u sustavu visokog obrazovanja

116
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:23,779
[SPEAKER_00] koje, pogotovo na ovim razinama

117
00:07:23,779 --> 00:07:26,040
[SPEAKER_00] društveno-humanističkog aspekta

118
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] je dosta zatvoreno

119
00:07:27,579 --> 00:07:29,399
[SPEAKER_00] i dosta statično, jel?

120
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:33,139
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila jedna razina

121
00:07:33,139 --> 00:07:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] mog, uvjetno rečeno,

122
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] dekanskog neuspjeha, jel?

123
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] A druga razina je naravno bila

124
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] ta koja se odnosi na te takozvane

125
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:44,819
[SPEAKER_00] kontroverzne stavove.

126
00:07:44,899 --> 00:07:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se mogu samo malo vraćati

127
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] sami ste rekli studenti vas pitaju

128
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:50,019
[SPEAKER_01] znači to su

129
00:07:50,019 --> 00:07:52,759
[SPEAKER_01] mladi ljudi od 18 godina pa na više

130
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:54,160
[SPEAKER_01] da li smiju koristiti AI?

131
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

132
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,680
[SPEAKER_01] To je znak više nego dobljam

133
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,259
[SPEAKER_01] da bi već u vrtiću se trebalo

134
00:07:58,259 --> 00:08:00,339
[SPEAKER_01] ovoj pozabaviti, jel?

135
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:04,660
[SPEAKER_01] Jer, mislim, svi, kući te šta hoću reći.

136
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:05,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zabaviti se već onda

137
00:08:05,779 --> 00:08:07,819
[SPEAKER_01] obišnjava djeci šta je to AI

138
00:08:07,819 --> 00:08:09,560
[SPEAKER_01] i koliko može koristiti, koliko ne.

139
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

140
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:14,040
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, obrazovanje je strukturan proces

141
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] i jako je pogrešno pojmanje

142
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:19,600
[SPEAKER_00] da se s obrazovanjem započinje, ne znam,

143
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,120
[SPEAKER_00] od prvog razda osnovne škole.

144
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] Činjenica je da se Republika Hrvatska

145
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:27,879
[SPEAKER_00] od svog osnutka, da tako kažem,

146
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] tražila u tom aspektu odgoja i obrazovanja

147
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:37,299
[SPEAKER_00] koji započinje u biti sa institucionalizacijom djece,

148
00:08:37,299 --> 00:08:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno sa onim trenutkom kada djete pošalješ

149
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:43,080
[SPEAKER_00] u neku, recimo, odgojnu instituciju

150
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,080
[SPEAKER_00] ili ti vrtić.

151
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] Pogrešno je razmišljanje

152
00:08:46,340 --> 00:08:48,399
[SPEAKER_00] da vrtići nemaju svoje programe,

153
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:50,820
[SPEAKER_00] da pedagoški standardi u vrtićima

154
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] također nisu dio određenih kurikula,

155
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] gdje mi imamo određene modele

156
00:08:56,460 --> 00:08:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] pedagoškog pristupa i u vrtićima.

157
00:08:59,779 --> 00:09:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam, recimo, i ja ostala iznenađena

158
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:06,100
[SPEAKER_00] kada je sin, kad mi je išao u vrtić,

159
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] kada sam shvatila da djete počelo gubiti na kilaži,

160
00:09:09,059 --> 00:09:10,299
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno da ne jede u vrtiću,

161
00:09:10,299 --> 00:09:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam pitala, pa dobro, u čemu je problem?

162
00:09:12,179 --> 00:09:14,740
[SPEAKER_00] I tad mi se reklo, a ne, znate,

163
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,259
[SPEAKER_00] mi imamo liberalan pristup,

164
00:09:17,019 --> 00:09:18,759
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo nikoga ni na što natjerat,

165
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:21,720
[SPEAKER_00] pa rekao, ok, ali zar ni na jedenje?

166
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ne u smislu tjeranja,

167
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego ok, ponudimo onda nešto drugo, jel?

168
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nije

169
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:29,580
[SPEAKER_00] u liberalnom odgoju,

170
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije pristup,

171
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] aha, želiš li se igrati?

172
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne želim,

173
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,379
[SPEAKER_00] u redu, onda sjedi na kauču

174
00:09:37,379 --> 00:09:39,100
[SPEAKER_00] i sjedi tamo do kraja radnog vremena.

175
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:41,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nego je liberalni pristup,

176
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] znači, hoćeš li se igrati s loptom

177
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] ili ćeš se igrati sa teniskim reketom.

178
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ti daš mogućnosti izbora,

179
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] ali on uvjetuje fizičku aktivnost

180
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] koja se događa između 10 i 11 sati.

181
00:09:54,059 --> 00:09:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] E, to je liberalan pristup

182
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji smo mi uspjeli na neki način

183
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] izvitoperiti

184
00:09:58,279 --> 00:10:00,639
[SPEAKER_00] i onda djeca iz tog sustava,

185
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] jel, dolaze u osnovnu školu,

186
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] osnovna škola je obavezna

187
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] u Republici Hrvatskoj,

188
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:07,120
[SPEAKER_00] ona ima zadan kurikul,

189
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali i određenu ležernost

190
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] baš zato što je obvezna.

191
00:10:10,779 --> 00:10:11,299
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

192
00:10:11,299 --> 00:10:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ne morate sada

193
00:10:13,259 --> 00:10:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] mijenjati na toj razini

194
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,120
[SPEAKER_00] nekakve pristupe,

195
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] vi ćete, na primjer,

196
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] promijeniti pristup

197
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] u takozvanoj cijelodnevnoj školi,

198
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] koju ja do jedne razine pozdravljam,

199
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:25,879
[SPEAKER_00] ali želim biti koji su njezini sadržaji,

200
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] a ne da to bude, ne znam,

201
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] sjedimo u čioni i gledamo filmove

202
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što smo napisali zadaču,

203
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:33,120
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

204
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,779
[SPEAKER_00] To mislim da nije dobar

205
00:10:35,779 --> 00:10:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] ni poticajan pristup, jel?

206
00:10:37,139 --> 00:10:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, činjenica je

207
00:10:40,299 --> 00:10:41,580
[SPEAKER_00] da ovi sadržaji,

208
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] medijska pismenost,

209
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] AI, kultura,

210
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:45,860
[SPEAKER_00] da tako kažem,

211
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] da bi trebali ući u koncepte

212
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] osnovnoškolskog obrazovanja,

213
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] e, ali to sad pokreće

214
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] jedan trom mehanizam

215
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi trebao promijeniti

216
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:57,399
[SPEAKER_00] kurikule vidjeti

217
00:10:57,399 --> 00:11:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] koje sadržaje, da tako kažemo,

218
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] isključiti,

219
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] a na njihovo mjesto

220
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] određene sadržaje uključiti,

221
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,299
[SPEAKER_00] što je uvijek problem.

222
00:11:06,299 --> 00:11:08,620
[SPEAKER_00] Iako, kada se gledaju

223
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:11,899
[SPEAKER_00] kurikuli srednjoškolskog obrazovanja,

224
00:11:11,899 --> 00:11:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo kad je strukovna škola

225
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] u pitanju,

226
00:11:15,139 --> 00:11:17,080
[SPEAKER_00] naprimjer, vrlo brzo su izbačeni

227
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] sadržaji povijesti

228
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:20,360
[SPEAKER_00] i geografije.

229
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,100
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovako,

230
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:23,179
[SPEAKER_00] bez ikakve široke

231
00:11:23,179 --> 00:11:24,379
[SPEAKER_00] javne rasprave,

232
00:11:24,379 --> 00:11:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] bilo čega,

233
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] s time što povijest u tom smislu

234
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] se i opet promatra,

235
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] kažem, statično,

236
00:11:30,179 --> 00:11:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] jer povijest može ponuditi

237
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] sadržaje baš o AI,

238
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu

239
00:11:34,539 --> 00:11:37,080
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je povijest umjetna inteligencija,

240
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako se razvijala umjetna inteligencija,

241
00:11:39,059 --> 00:11:40,799
[SPEAKER_00] ali ona se razvija za njih pet godina.

242
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:42,740
[SPEAKER_00] Početci njezinog razvoja

243
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] su tamo 1960. godina,

244
00:11:44,779 --> 00:11:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] već kreće koncept razmišljanja

245
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] o umjetnoj inteligenciji.

246
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] E, pa, i to povijestničar

247
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] može pripremiti kao sadržaj,

248
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] ako mu se dozvoli.

249
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] Iako, da, gazda je u Bruselu dobro.

250
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mogu biti malo sarkastičan,

251
00:11:59,940 --> 00:12:02,179
[SPEAKER_01] ali misli da to vodi tome.

252
00:12:02,179 --> 00:12:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, mi jesmo dio

253
00:12:03,779 --> 00:12:07,120
[SPEAKER_00] određene društveno-političke strukture.

254
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] dio smo određene političke unije.

255
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kako god bilo,

256
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] mi to ne možemo ignorirati.

257
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,799
[SPEAKER_00] Bez obzira što se tu govori

258
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:18,379
[SPEAKER_00] o jednom obliku isto tako,

259
00:12:18,379 --> 00:12:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći, realno labavih sustava,

260
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] pa jedan dio imate zadržan

261
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,639
[SPEAKER_00] kao nacionalnu komponentu

262
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,080
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj samo vi odlučujete,

263
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali tako, međutim,

264
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,419
[SPEAKER_00] sve to podložno

265
00:12:30,419 --> 00:12:33,139
[SPEAKER_00] određenoj reviziji.

266
00:12:33,139 --> 00:12:34,580
[SPEAKER_01] Kontrola nikad veća.

267
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:36,399
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je revizija dozvoljena.

268
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,860
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, opropo tih kontroveznih izjava,

269
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:42,399
[SPEAKER_01] među revno je ovaj

270
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:44,700
[SPEAKER_01] dosta drugih kontroveznih izjava

271
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:45,679
[SPEAKER_01] je palo vodu poput

272
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:47,860
[SPEAKER_01] Logarovu, Jasenovcu, Žrtvama,

273
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:49,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer bili smo u ovoj svjedoci.

274
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:50,559
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, vaše mišljenje o tome.

275
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ipak ste izgledali bili u pravu, jel?

276
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,240
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa ovako, ja priznam.

277
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, pa jeste, nikom je ništa.

278
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa...

279
00:12:58,039 --> 00:13:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] Nikom je ništa, ovaj, da je sa drugoj strane,

280
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:01,720
[SPEAKER_01] je od desnog spektra,

281
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:04,759
[SPEAKER_01] to je bilo ono, šov 24 sata.

282
00:13:04,759 --> 00:13:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nikom je ništa.

283
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] Velika izgleda laž.

284
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:08,179
[SPEAKER_01] Moram ja sad priznati,

285
00:13:08,179 --> 00:13:09,100
[SPEAKER_01] to je izgleda bila laž,

286
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji su i mene učili u sve školi,

287
00:13:10,539 --> 00:13:11,580
[SPEAKER_01] srednje školi,

288
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:12,759
[SPEAKER_01] broju žrtava je pala.

289
00:13:13,220 --> 00:13:14,720
[SPEAKER_01] Šaptom je pala u vodu

290
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,799
[SPEAKER_01] i reakcije su onako bile.

291
00:13:16,799 --> 00:13:18,840
[SPEAKER_01] Da nije bilo tako nekih stotinjak ljudi

292
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] koji su to objavljivali po društvenim mrežama,

293
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:23,899
[SPEAKER_01] prošlo bi gotovo nezamjećeno.

294
00:13:23,899 --> 00:13:24,580
[SPEAKER_01] Ne se slažete?

295
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:25,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

296
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:29,379
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ja moram reći jednu također istinu.

297
00:13:29,379 --> 00:13:33,879
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto da se shvati problem.

298
00:13:33,879 --> 00:13:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da se razumije koliko je zapravo problem širok.

299
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću možda upasti

300
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:45,320
[SPEAKER_00] i u jedan mali segment teorije zavjere,

301
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:49,240
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne vjerujem u nekakve teoretičare zavjere.

302
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] To je danas in, ne sekirajte se.

303
00:13:51,059 --> 00:13:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

304
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:55,919
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vjerujem, definitivno vjerujem u strukture

305
00:13:55,919 --> 00:13:59,320
[SPEAKER_00] koje su zapravo čuvari sustava

306
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] i koje valjda brinu

307
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se taj sustav ne promijeni prebrzo,

308
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] da zapravo ide kronološki,

309
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] da bude kronološki dugog trajanja,

310
00:14:11,100 --> 00:14:11,720
[SPEAKER_00] što se kaže.

311
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:15,600
[SPEAKER_00] Prije svega, kada govorimo o Jasenovcu,

312
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:20,120
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Jasenovac i ja,

313
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] u tom smislu nekakve poveznice,

314
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo nemamo nikakvu poveznicu.

315
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] Naime, ja se u istraživačkom smislu

316
00:14:28,340 --> 00:14:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] uopće ne bavim Jasenovcem,

317
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:35,419
[SPEAKER_00] ali je to kao jedna anatema

318
00:14:35,419 --> 00:14:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] iskorišteno u trenutku kada se mene trebalo eliminirati

319
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] kao dekanicu.

320
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, procijenjeno je od strane te strukture

321
00:14:47,519 --> 00:14:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] za koju ja još dan danas nisam.

322
00:14:49,779 --> 00:14:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam otprilike ključne aktere

323
00:14:52,679 --> 00:14:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji su mene napadali,

324
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:59,419
[SPEAKER_00] koji su napravili cijeli jedan difamacijski koncept.

325
00:14:59,419 --> 00:15:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, riječ je o jednom udruženju,

326
00:15:02,539 --> 00:15:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] sad hoćemo li ih nazvati zločinačkim udruženjem

327
00:15:05,259 --> 00:15:05,899
[SPEAKER_00] kako god,

328
00:15:05,899 --> 00:15:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali je činjenica da je nekoliko ljudi

329
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,200
[SPEAKER_00] sudjelovalo u tom projektu.

330
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja znam samo ključne aktere,

331
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, ajmo reći onu cijelu mašineriju

332
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:17,120
[SPEAKER_00] koja se iza toga nalazila,

333
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali oni su iskoristili Jasenovac

334
00:15:20,039 --> 00:15:22,799
[SPEAKER_00] kao vrlo osjetljivo pitanje

335
00:15:22,799 --> 00:15:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] da mene difamiraju.

336
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] Iako kažem, ja se u znanstveno

337
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,820
[SPEAKER_00] istraživačkom smislu Jasenovcem

338
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] uopće ne bavim.

339
00:15:30,659 --> 00:15:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] Poput, na primjer, Kojića, Banića,

340
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] poput doktorice Blanke Matković,

341
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,620
[SPEAKER_00] koja se zaista bavi,

342
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] Stipe Pilića,

343
00:15:40,139 --> 00:15:41,580
[SPEAKER_00] koji su se stvarno bavili

344
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] istraživački Jasenovcem.

345
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,919
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se nikada nisam bavila

346
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] istraživački Jasenovcem.

347
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se usudila baviti Jasenovcem

348
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] na razini memorije,

349
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kulture sjećanja

350
00:15:54,519 --> 00:15:56,879
[SPEAKER_00] i to više u kontekstu

351
00:15:56,879 --> 00:15:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] onog uklanjanja

352
00:15:58,399 --> 00:16:00,600
[SPEAKER_00] hosove ploče

353
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:01,879
[SPEAKER_00] u Jasenovcu,

354
00:16:01,879 --> 00:16:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] koja zapravo nema veze

355
00:16:02,860 --> 00:16:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] sa spomem područjem Jasenovac,

356
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego koja ima veze

357
00:16:07,019 --> 00:16:09,240
[SPEAKER_00] s Jasenovcem kao mjestom.

358
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,899
[SPEAKER_00] E, u tom smislu,

359
00:16:10,899 --> 00:16:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] kada je bila korona,

360
00:16:12,659 --> 00:16:14,759
[SPEAKER_00] imala sam jednu objavu

361
00:16:14,759 --> 00:16:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] na svom Facebooku,

362
00:16:16,519 --> 00:16:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam rekla da je Jasenovac

363
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] ostao zapravo mjesto razilaženja,

364
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] a da bi on trebao postati mjesto spajanja,

365
00:16:25,340 --> 00:16:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] zato što pod svim onim silnim mjerama,

366
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] ostanite kod kuće,

367
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte izlaziti van i tako dalje.

368
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:34,120
[SPEAKER_00] U Jasenovcu je održana

369
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] tradicionalna komemoracija

370
00:16:36,019 --> 00:16:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] za žrtve Jasenovce.

371
00:16:38,059 --> 00:16:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se ja postavila pitanje sa malo,

372
00:16:40,519 --> 00:16:40,919
[SPEAKER_00] zašto?

373
00:16:40,919 --> 00:16:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne može se komemorirati ništa drugo,

374
00:16:43,759 --> 00:16:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovo može.

375
00:16:44,919 --> 00:16:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kako su to sad principi

376
00:16:46,059 --> 00:16:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] i čemu to sve?

377
00:16:47,700 --> 00:16:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] I to je, dakle,

378
